   <meta>
      <dc:title xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">keep-content-with-border</dc:title>
      <dc:description xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Tests that pages are not broken between a border of a block and the content of that block. Tested with keep="page", orphans or widows on the block with the border. Also tested for two nested blocks with borders.</dc:description>
